#: src/users/02-media.md:5
msgid ""
"The main type of content in Lemmy is text which can be formatted with "
"Markdown. Refer to the table below for supported formatting rules. The Lemmy "
"user interface also provides buttons for formatting, so it's not necessary "
"to remember all of it. You can also follow the interactive [CommonMark "
"tutorial](https://commonmark.org/help/tutorial/) to get started."
